OL,3,CScottish Borders nurse named 'Nurse of
OL,4,Cthe Year' at national awards
OL,6,FA Scottish Borders nurse has been
OL,7,Fnamed "Nurse of the Year" at a
OL,8,Fnational awards ceremony.
OL,10,FLynsey Russell, who works as a senior
OL,11,Fcharge nurse at received the award at
OL,12,Fthe Royal College of Nursing Scotland
OL,13,FAwards. Lynsey also received the
OL,14,FClinical Leadership Award.
OL,16,FWorking in the intensive therapy unit,
OL,17,FLynsey has led on several projects
OL,18,Faimed at both enhancing patient care
OL,19,Fand improving staff wellbeing.
