OL,3,CScottish Borders nurse named 'Nurse of
OL,4,Cthe Year' at national awards
OL,6,FShe was nominated by her colleagues
OL,7,Ffor the award who described her as
OL,8,Fcommitted and passionate about
OL,9,Fintensive care nursing.
OL,11,FThe judges said her work showcased the
OL,12,Fvery best of nursing in Scotland.
OL,14,FAlso from , Rachel Gardiner won the
OL,15,FLearning Disability Award.
OL,17,FThis was in part to her work raising
OL,18,Fawareness about the need for better
OL,19,Fsupport for people with learning
OL,20,Fdisabilities in the justice system.
