OL,3,CScottish Borders nurse named 'Nurse of
OL,4,Cthe Year' at national awards
OL,6,FSarah Horan, Director of Nursing,
OL,7,FMidwifery and Allied Health
OL,8,FProfessionals at NHS Borders, said:
OL,9,F"We are absolutely delighted that
OL,10,FLynsey and Rachel won the awards they
OL,11,Fwere nominated for at the RCN awards
OL,12,Fon Thursday night.
OL,14,F"They are both worthy winners and
OL,15,Fdeserve to be recognised for their
OL,16,Fhard work and dedication. We are
OL,17,Fincredibly proud of them both.
OL,19,F"Lynsey also winning the RCN Nurse of
OL,20,Fthe Year title is a truly magnificent
OL,21,Fachievement.
